      "role": "user",
      "content": "counseling? what's that going to do? it's just more talking, more explaining myself to someone who won't actually understand how much this sucks. it's just another thing on my to-do list that i don't have the energy for. i'm not just \"stressed\"... it feels like the version of me that actually cares about things is just dead. there's no \"moving forward\" when there's nothing left to move toward.",
